{# 
    Details (<details>)
    ===========================================================================

    Defines additional details that the user can view or hide.

    Variables:
    - `details_summary`: The summary or title for the details section. Defaults to "More Information".
    - `details_content`: The content inside the details section. Defaults to "Default details content".

    Notes:
    - The `| e` filter is used to escape any special characters in the variables to prevent XSS attacks.

    Links:
    - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details
    - https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_details.asp

#}

<details>
    <summary>{{ details_summary | default('More Information') | e }}</summary>
    <p>{{ details_content | default('Default details content') | e }}</p>
</details>
